{"tid":2124530,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★日本餐廳奇招防疫　恐怖假人公仔陪坐食飯超驚嚇","createTime":"2020-07-25T12:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T15:41:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b17e7b53b7d51f82c2e78bbd8465f2bdd5e5fca5","tid":2124530,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200725/363684603489292288.jpeg/PF5E2od-8Li20Tq8Gk3k78ZmelNVbyNfh29Mi4dvTIs?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200725%2F363684603489292288.jpeg%2FPF5E2od-8Li20Tq8Gk3k78ZmelNVbyNfh29Mi4dvTIs%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=8fe44a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200725/363658099606818816.jpeg/bJS1X1vD2aArDZMS0cw3y2yJ0GyEpemcsYxitrGMYrY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200725%2F363658099606818816.jpeg%2FbJS1X1vD2aArDZMS0cw3y2yJ0GyEpemcsYxitrGMYrY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2d4776b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東京一間中華料理店「麒麟菜館」最近成為網民熱討話題，當地媒體最近訪問餐廳負責人，指自疫情爆發以來，生意一落千丈，而且場面越見冷清，加上政府呼籲餐廳隔開客人座位，遂以具創意的方法防疫。<br />\n<br />\n餐廳負責人相當有心思找來10多個男女假人模特兒，又為他們穿上不同服裝並坐在不同位置，打算令餐廳氣氛變得熱鬧。不過來到的客人卻發現，每個假人的表情亦非常詭異，坐在旁邊更有種不寒而懍的感覺，令客人們感到無比的尷尬，更坦言好像有種奇異的眼光看着自己吃飯一樣。<br />\n<br />\n網民亦笑言餐廳負責人的做法太創新，「是在趕客吧」、「快笑死了」、「吃飯也感到極尷尬」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/502481/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E5%A5%87%E6%8B%9B%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB-%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%81%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94%E9%99%AA%E5%9D%90%E9%A3%9F%E9%A3%AF%E8%B6%85%E9%A9%9A%E5%9A%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F502481%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%25A4%2590%