一樣。<br />\n<br />\n網民亦笑言餐廳負責人的做法太創新，「是在趕客吧」、「快笑死了」、「吃飯也感到極尷尬」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/502481/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E5%A5%87%E6%8B%9B%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB-%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%81%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94%E9%99%AA%E5%9D%90%E9%A3%9F%E9%A3%AF%E8%B6%85%E9%A9%9A%E5%9A%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F502481%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E5%25A5%2587%25E6%258B%259B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E5%2581%2587%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%2599%25AA%25E5%259D%2590%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%25A9%259A%25E5%259A%2587&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=ab561d18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/502481/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E5%A5%87%E6%8B%9B%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB-%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%81%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94%E9%99%AA%E5%9D%90%E9%A3%9F%E9%A3%AF%E8%B6%85%E9%A9%9A%E5%9A%87</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:08:40.000Z","msg":"借位求 pin<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mi5.gov.uk/modal_forms/nojs/webform/363\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mi5.gov.uk%2Fmodal_forms%2Fnojs%2Fwebform%2F363&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=7c8a204c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mi5.gov.uk/modal_forms/nojs/webform/363</a><br />\n國際清算第一彈<br />\nI noticed on social media that a Hong Kong police and his wife have both acquired British National (Overseas) passport. I believe that they cause a serious threat to the national security of the UK.<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong police is notorious for executing the national security law in Hong Kong, as well as oppressing Hongkongers during incidents meticulously documented by the international media. The Hong Kong police not only undermines freedom in Hong Kong, but also conducts human rights abuses and helps the CCP conduct oppression breaching the Sino-British Joint Declaration. The couple may conduct espionage and propaganda activities detrimental to the national security of the UK.<br />\n<br />\nBelow are the social media links which I found:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Samhon852/status/1278351828388700160?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSamhon852%2Fstatus%2F1278351828388700160%3Fs%3D20&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=bf410bd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSamhon852%2Fstatus%2F1278351828388700160%3Fs%3D20&h=5b5d5fb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Samhon852/status/1278351828388700160?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2090313/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2090313/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lihkgpig/posts/287216626025204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flihkgpig%2Fposts%2F287216626025204&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=12e3896c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lihkgpig/posts/287216626025204</a><br />\n<br />\nI hope that this couple will be arrested upon arrival to the UK, and the information can be shared to other intelligence agencies among the Five Eyes international alliance. This is a great step to stop the Chinese Communist Party from extending its spy network through these pro-CCP anti-democracy immigrants. Thanks a lot for your attention!"},{"pid":"5d18de5819011103e47674e7337b4e3cda0b6a34","tid":2124530,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"<